decision_conditions:
&lt;p&gt;Soundproofing shall be provided such that any rooms of the 2 residential units sharing a party wall with a commercial use, shall receive a minimum airborne sound insulation on the party element which achieves DnT&#x27;w of 60 dB before the first use of the development hereby approved. The soundproofing shall be retained thereafter in perpetuity.
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
REASON: To ensure that potential occupiers do not suffer a loss of amenity by reason of noise nuisance and other excess noise from activities within any adjoining commercial premises.&lt;/p&gt;
